data.description: Come view this well-kept 3 bed 2 bath home located in South Jackson. Minutes away from HWY 45 bypass, with easy access to town. All black appliances, new paint, new mulch, and so much more! Roof and HVAC replaced in 2022. Chain link fence surrounding back yard and a wood stove inside makes for a cozy fall night. Seller is providing a home warranty for the future homeowner.
